- Prompt engine types: `packages/prompt-engine/src/types.ts:60-103`
- Settings sub-page pattern: `apps/app/src/app/(app)/(org)/[slug]/(manage)/settings/api-keys/`
- Inngest function pattern: `api/platform/src/inngest/functions/ingest-delivery.ts`
- Token helpers: `api/platform/src/lib/token-helpers.ts:14-70`

